room_title: Escape room "Davy Jones' Locker" by Escape in 60 in Charleston
review: Great time. We did Davy Jone's Locker and it was certainly a challenge but a good time. Would recommend to tourist and locals alike.

room_title: Escape room "Davy Jones' Locker" by Escape in 60 in Charleston
review: We only had three in our group, and we did the room Dave Jones' Locker. We made it out with only 6 minutes to spare. Had a great time.

room_title: Escape room "Davy Jones' Locker" by Escape in 60 in Charleston
review: Escape in 60 had good, unique mechanics in Davy Jones Locker. I was very happy with the escape room.

room_title: Escape room "Davy Jones' Locker" by Escape in 60 in Charleston
review: The Davey Jones locker room was so much fun! Our first escape room ever and it was fun for the whole family. We are all very competitive so we pretty much had to get it together to finally escape in 48 minutes!Our ages ranged from adult to teens to a 6-year-old (which by the way helped around a clue).

room_title: Escape room "Davy Jones' Locker" by Escape in 60 in Charleston
review: I was just walking around with my bestie and her baby (less than 6 months) trying to escape the heat when we came across this gem! It was simple to just walk-in, book the next available room and start. We did the Pirate room with us 2.5 and another 2 strangers, which we finished with 10+ minutes to spare! It was loads of fun. The question/answer system was easy, and the people working there were really nice!
